His excellency the president of Nigeria, president Buhari is reportedly present in Ebonyi State for the commissioning of projects.
According to 92.3 Nigeria info Radio Station in Port Harcourt on Thursday, the 5th of May 2022, Mr President would be spending two days in the above mentioned state so he could carry out the commissioning program of about sixteen (16) projects in Ebonyi State.
Due to his visit to the state, there have been lots of comments following his appearance. Since Ebonyi is an Eastern State which belong to the Igbo ethnic group, Mr President wore the symbol of the Igbo people which is the ‘Isi Agu’ dress.
Recall that the president also wore similar dress when he visited another Eastern State of Igbo’s origin. He was heavily critizied on the social media following his trouser’s fashion.
And so, here are the comments on the latest president Buhari’s appearance in Ebonyi State.This one said, the tailor has learnt his lesson following the previous trouser he made that spiked comments all over the social media platforms.
However, the second persons wants to see the trouser’s full length to be sure the previous mistake was not repeated.


